data.description:
Discover refined living in this impeccably maintained 2 bedroom, 2 1/2 bathroom end-unit Siena model townhouse. From the moment you step into this meticulously cared-for home, you'll be captivated by the immaculate condition and thoughtful design. Golden streams of natural light gracefully cascade through the windows illuminating the space with warmth and vibrancy.The heart of this residence is the updated kitchen, featuring maple cabinets, granite counters, a breakfast bar, and a suite of GE stainless steel appliances (approximately 5 years old). Modern touches like recessed lighting and an updated kitchen faucet add a touch of sophistication to the space. The first floor, elegantly tiled, seamlessly flows into the warmth of the second floor adorned with beautiful hardwood flooring. Upstairs, the spacious bedrooms offer a haven of comfort, each equipped with walk-in closets featuring built-in shelving, updated ceiling fans, and recessed lighting. A large loft located between the bedrooms could be used as a 3rd. The bathrooms have been tastefully updated, showcasing contemporary sinks and vanities. The master bath boasts wood-look tile flooring and a stone-accented shower.

Step outside onto the screened-in lanai, where tranquility meets comfort, overlooking a secluded rear yard. The perfect spot to unwind and enjoy the serenity of your surroundings. Additional features include garage storage, a laundry area with a Samsung washer/dryer (approx. 5 years old). Window blinds and treatments convey. Amenities include clubhouse, fitness center, 2 pools, playgrounds, tennis/pickleball, and basketball. Seller has paid the roof assessment in full.

This home is a testament to the owners' detail-oriented care and is an oasis of perfection. Don't miss the opportunity to call this meticulously maintained townhouse your home.
